            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1947-12-30T18:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-12-31T00:00:00-05:00" n="349" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d349">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>At its 69th Meeting, August 30, 1947, the Allied Control Council discussed the
                    new level of industry plan for the American and British zones of occupation. For
                    a report on the meeting, see telegram 3006, September 1, from Berlin, <ref target="#pg_1067">page 1067</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
